                                    "comments": "Please see also : \"EMA/267448/2012 - EMEA/H/A-30/1264 : Assessment report pursuant to Article 30 of Directive 2001/83/EC, as amended - FEMARA and Associated Names (letrozole), 22-May-2012 (IDRAC <Link type=\"Regulatory\" id=\"145038\">145038</Link>)\".",
