                                    "comments": "This document replaces the previous version of the EPAR on PREZISTA (darunavir): EMEA/H/C/000707 Revision 31 (IDRAC <Link type=\"Regulatory\" id=\"191341\">191341</Link>). \r\n\r\nNB: This exclusive document has been prepared integrating the files released in English by the EMA into one comprehensive document. Consequently, the page numbering is not in sequence, but has been left so that the user can appreciate the reorganisation. It is also enriched by a detailed Table of Contents provided in the left frame.",
                                    "dateDisplay": "28-Nov-2014",
